      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain you feel is not just sadness but a profound sense of loss, and it is important to acknowledge that your feelings are valid. However, choosing to end your life is not a solution to the darkness you are facing, as there are people who can help you navigate through this difficult time. Please consider reaching out to a crisis hotline or a mental health professional who can provide support and guidance. You are not alone, and there is hope for a different perspective.",
